[wait time="4.0"]
yuna: We land.
yuna: Sit in the field.
yuna: Overcast sky but not threatening.
yuna: In the distance, the city's silhouette — buildings still standing among the ones that have already fallen.
[wait time="2.0"]
[signal arg="start convo grass field"]
join yuna (Outlined) left
yuna: Baku. Have you heard about the alpha?
join baku (DarkenedOutlined) right
update baku (Outlined)
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
baku: .....
baku: Where'd you hear that?
update baku (DarkenedOutlined)
update yuna (Outlined)
yuna: The briefing before I was sent here.
yuna: It was mentioned briefly — a monster with size and power beyond normal classification.
yuna: Possibly the source of all the spawns in this city.
update baku (Outlined)
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
baku: (looks at the sky)
baku: I've seen it once. Long time ago.
update baku (DarkenedOutlined)
update yuna (Outlined)
yuna: And?
yuna: What does the creature look like?
update baku (Outlined)
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
baku: Big.
update baku (DarkenedOutlined)
update yuna (Outlined)
yuna: Define big.
update baku (Outlined)
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
baku: (thinks for a moment)
baku: Reeeeeaaaaaaally big!
update baku (DarkenedOutlined)
update yuna (Outlined)
yuna: (exhales)
yuna: That is not helpful at all.
update baku (Outlined)
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
