yuna: If I can bring proof that I defeated the alpha  —
yuna: — the association will reconsider lifting my banishment...
baku: (turns)
join baku (Outlined) right
baku: That's your plan?
join yuna (Outlined) left
update baku (DarkenedOutlined)
yuna: It's the only plan that makes sense.
